OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLocally
OL,6,Fheavy overnight rain clearing.
OL,7,FSaturday cooler, mainly cloudy but
OL,8,Fwest coast brightening up. Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday dry with some sunshine at
OL,10,Ftimes, especially Monday, and turning
OL,11,Fwarmer again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
